Package smarthome.mapper.mapper

Class ActuatorMapper

java.lang.Object
smarthome.mapper.mapper.ActuatorMapper
@Component public class ActuatorMapper extends Object
ActuatorMapper is a class for mapping ActuatorDTO to ActuatorMap and vice versa.
